* 张量和场操作
* 人类可读的偏微分方程离散化语法
* [[线性系统|线性系统]]求解<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.openfoam.com/features/linear-solvers.php |title=Linear system solvers in OpenFOAM |accessdate=2012-07-17 |archive-date=2012-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120723001443/http://www.openfoam.com/features/linear-solvers.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>
